## Measuring Journey Success

### Key Performance Indicators by Stage

**Awareness and Research (Stage 1-2):**
- Website traffic and engagement metrics
- Content consumption and sharing rates
- Speaking engagement and thought leadership impact
- Brand awareness and recognition measurement

**Evaluation and Engagement (Stage 3-4):**
- Consultation-to-proposal conversion rates
- Proposal win rates and average deal size
- Sales cycle length and efficiency
- Client onboarding satisfaction and time-to-value

**Delivery and Completion (Stage 5-6):**
- Project delivery timeline and budget performance
- Client satisfaction and Net Promoter Score
- Scope change and issue resolution effectiveness
- Knowledge transfer and capability building success

**Advocacy and Growth (Stage 7):**
- Client retention and expansion rates
- Referral generation and conversion
- Case study and testimonial development
- Industry recognition and award achievement

